summary: Implements the Moto mock for AWS EC2 Managed Prefix Lists, defining a resource model with ARN and owner information and a backend that supports creation, deletion, description, entry retrieval, and modification of managed prefix list resources, including tag handling and filtering.
business_intent: Enable developers to test interactions with EC2 Managed Prefix List APIs without accessing real AWS by providing an inâ€‘memory simulation of the full lifecycle of managed prefix lists.
